Enclosing class:
JsLocation
protected abstract static class JsLocation.Members
extends DOM.Location.Prototype.Members

An internal class containing membership data for its enclosing opaque class.

This class is only used inside of opaque or internal classes or class members.

Author:
J.J.Liu (Jianjun Liu) at http://www.jscripter.org
JavaScript:
Re-compilers must report error on resolving an internal class.
